charts). COLLISION DETECTION: All create/move/fit-to-range operations 
automatically check for overlaps with data and other charts. Warnings are 
returned in the result message if collisions are detected. Always verify layout 
with screenshot(capture-sheet) after creating charts. CHART TYPES: 70\u002B 
types available including Column, Line, Pie, Bar, Area, XY Scatter. CREATE 
OPTIONS: - create-from-range: Create from cell range (e.g., \u0027A1:D10\u0027) 
- create-from-table: Create from Excel Table (uses table\u0027s data range) - 
